How to play 42 Battles

>move with arrows
>press space to attack (first attack)
>press "z" to use secondary attack
>press "p" to enter menu

>To win you need to kill all enemies

>What you get on each lvl:
>lvl 1 first attack
>lvl 2 attack speed
>lvl 3 damage increase
>lvl 4 secondary attack
>lvl 5 attack damage

Have fun :)